Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Just a little more time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:40.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Let's stay together，my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:44.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Won't you tell me why
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:49.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Let me know what makes you cry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:53.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}One day in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:58.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Don't you know things can change，my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:02.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Won't you dry your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:07.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Someday you will find your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:12.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Shining，jumping，singing，dreaming，growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:15.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}So just the way you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:19.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Here's my heart，no need to hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:24.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}'Cause no one can take away your right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:29.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}In every case，you can break througe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:33.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Realize，I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:37.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Here's my heart，no need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:42.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}The stars above，shine bright in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:47.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Just call my name if you're feeling blue
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18\fad(100,100)\i1}Cheer up，I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:55.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs22\fad(100,100)}Here's your heart，I'm not feeling lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:23:02.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs22\fad(100,100)}We can make it，hope our dreams will all come true
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:09.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs22\fad(100,100)}Go on，smile for you and me
